==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spiteful
<hw>Spite"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Filled with, or
showing, spite; having a desire to vex, annoy, or injure; malignant;
malicious; <as>as, a <ex>spiteful</ex> person or act</as>.</def>
<au>Shak.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Spite"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<wf>Spite"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spitfire</ent>⟦br⟧
